HM-GM-AM-QM inequalities.
For $x_0, x_1, \cdots, x_{n-1} \in \mathbb{R}^{+}$:
$$
\begin{align}
0 < & \frac{n}{\frac{1}{x_0} + \frac{1}{x_1} + \cdots + \frac{1}{x_{n-1}} } \\
 \le & (x_0 x_1 \cdots x_{n-1})^{\frac{1}{n}} \\
\le & \frac{x_0 + x_1 + \cdots + x_{n-1}}{n} \\
\le & (\frac{x_0^2 + x_1^2 + \cdots + x_{n-1}^2}{n})^{\frac{1}{2}}
\end{align}
$$
